The paper deals with analyzing and predicting complex behavior in social networks using Call Detail Record (CDR) datasets. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SOC) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves analyzing and modeling user behavior, which could fall under the Cybersecurity (cs.CR) or Cybercrime (cs.CYBER) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also involves feature extraction and analysis, which could fall under the Databases (cs.DB) sub-category.
